#8217;editor di WordPress per pubblicare su internet&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/olbia-wordpress-meetup/events/292437552/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 19 apr, ore 18:30 &#8220;Community WordPress: special guest Isotta Peira&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/292210223/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 21 apr, ore 18:00 &#8220;Tutto quello che volevi sapere su ChatGPT&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/RomaWordPress/events/292321068\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity is-style-dots\" style=\"margin-top:33px;margin-bottom:33px\" />\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center is-style-serif has-blueberry-3-background-color has-background\">&#8230; articolo  in  aggiornamento: saranno aggiunte altre date di altri meetup, torna a leggere questo articolo nei prossimi giorni&#8230;</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://it.wordpress.org/news/2023/04/meetup-di-aprile-2023/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_bas